HEADWORD: Contradistinguish
<hw>Con`tra*dis*tin"guish</hw> <pr>(?; 144)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Contradistinguished</conjf>
